---
// Figure: Real opt in versus soft compulsion
// Two simple paths converging on the same service outcome.
// Side list of six friction points that convert a voluntary system
// into one that is coercive in practice.
---

<div class="reveal my-12 md:my-16">
  <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border overflow-hidden" style="background: rgba(11,11,17,0.6);">
    <div class="p-6 md:p-8">

      <div class="mb-6">
        <p class="text-text-tertiary text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-1">Access to service</p>
        <h3 class="text-text-primary font-display font-bold text-lg tracking-tight">Real opt in versus soft compulsion</h3>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[1.35fr,1fr] gap-5 md:gap-6 items-center">

        <!-- Path diagram -->
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border/60 p-4 md:p-5" style="background: rgba(11,11,17,0.4);">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 460 340" class="w-full" role="img" aria-label="Two paths — digital and decline — both reaching the same service outcome. Friction accumulates on the decline path when a system is voluntary in law but coercive in practice.">
            <defs>
              <marker id="ovs-arrow" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="9" refY="5" markerWidth="7" markerHeight="7" orient="auto-start-reverse">
                <path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="rgba(232,232,240,0.6)"/>
              </marker>
            </defs>

            <!-- Start -->
            <rect x="130" y="20" width="200" height="42" rx="8" fill="rgba(167,139,250,0.08)" stroke="rgba(167,139,250,0.55)" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            <text x="230" y="45" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,232,240,0.85)" font-family="'Syne', system-ui" font-size="12" font-weight="600">Citizen needs a service</text>

            <line x1="230" y1="62" x2="230" y2="80" stroke="rgba(167,139,250,0.4)" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            <line x1="230" y1="80" x2="110" y2="110" stroke="rgba(167,139,250,0.4)" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            <line x1="230" y1="80" x2="350" y2="110" stroke="rgba(167,139,250,0.4)" stroke-width="1.2"/>

            <!-- Digital path -->
            <rect x="30" y="115" width="160" height="42" rx="8" fill="rgba(74,222,128,0.08)" stroke="rgba(74,222,128,0.55)" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            <text x="110" y="140" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,232,240,0.9)" font-family="'Syne', system-ui" font-size="12" font-weight="600">Digital path</text>

            <line x1="110" y1="157" x2="110" y2="180" stroke="rgba(74,222,128,0.5)" stroke-width="1.2" marker-end="url(#ovs-arrow)"/>
            <rect x="30" y="185" width="160" height="42" rx="8" fill="rgba(74,222,128,0.05)" stroke="rgba(74,222,128,0.4)" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            <text x="110" y="210" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,232,240,0.8)" font-family="'Syne', system-ui" font-size="12">Verify · present · proceed</text>

            <!-- Decline path -->
            <rect x="270" y="115" width="160" height="42" rx="8" fill="rgba(245,158,11,0.08)" stroke="rgba(245,158,11,0.55)" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            <text x="350" y="140" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,232,240,0.9)" font-family="'Syne', system-ui" font-size="12" font-weight="600">Decline path</text>

            <line x1="350" y1="157" x2="350" y2="180" stroke="rgba(245,158,11,0.5)" stroke-width="1.2" marker-end="url(#ovs-arrow)"/>
            <rect x="270" y="185" width="160" height="42" rx="8" fill="rgba(245,158,11,0.05)" stroke="rgba(245,158,11,0.4)" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            <text x="350" y="210" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,232,240,0.8)" font-family="'Syne', system-ui" font-size="12">Alternative · assisted</text>

            <!-- Converge -->
            <line x1="110" y1="227" x2="230" y2="265" stroke="rgba(74,222,128,0.45)" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            <line x1="350" y1="227" x2="230" y2="265" stroke="rgba(245,158,11,0.45)" stroke-width="1.2"/>

            <rect x="100" y="270" width="260" height="48" rx="8" fill="rgba(74,222,128,0.1)" stroke="rgba(74,222,128,0.6)" stroke-width="1.3"/>
            <text x="230" y="292" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,232,240,0.9)" font-family="'Syne', system-ui" font-size="12" font-weight="600">Equal service outcome</text>
            <text x="230" y="307" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,232,240,0.55)" font-family="'Inter', system-ui" font-size="10">the test for a real opt in</text>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <!-- Friction points -->
        <div>
          <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-3" style="color: rgba(245,158,11,0.75);">Where voluntary becomes coercive</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">
            <li class="grid grid-cols-[1.4rem,1fr] gap-2 items-start"><span class="font-mono text-xs mt-0.5 text-text-tertiary">01</span><span>Extra time at every step</span></li>
            <li class="grid grid-cols-[1.4rem,1fr] gap-2 items-start"><span class="font-mono text-xs mt-0.5 text-text-tertiary">02</span><span>Repeated checks and re-verification</span></li>
            <li class="grid grid-cols-[1.4rem,1fr] gap-2 items-start"><span class="font-mono text-xs mt-0.5 text-text-tertiary">03</span><span>Lower quality service from the non-digital route</span></li>
            <li class="grid grid-cols-[1.4rem,1fr] gap-2 items-start"><span class="font-mono text-xs mt-0.5 text-text-tertiary">04</span><span>Exception queues and escalation bottlenecks</span></li>
            <li class="grid grid-cols-[1.4rem,1fr] gap-2 items-start"><span class="font-mono text-xs mt-0.5 text-text-tertiary">05</span><span>Manual handling dependent on staff discretion</span></li>
            <li class="grid grid-cols-[1.4rem,1fr] gap-2 items-start"><span class="font-mono text-xs mt-0.5 text-text-tertiary">06</span><span>Inaccessible support</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="text-text-tertiary text-xs mt-3 text-center italic">
    A system can be voluntary in statute and coercive in operation. Opt out is only real when the declining path reaches the same outcome.
  </p>
</div>
